I.R.C. § 45E(e)(4)Increased Credit For Certain Small Employers—In the case of an employer which would be an eligible employer under subsection (c)
                     if section 408(p)(2)(C)(i) was applied by substituting “50 employees” for “100 employees”,
                     subsection (a) shall be applied by substituting “100 percent” for “50 percent”.
